This product includes software developed independently as a clean-room
TypeScript reimplementation of the public API surface of the Mastra
framework (https://mastra.ai). Redtuma is not affiliated with, endorsed
by, or derived from the Mastra source code. Behavioral conformance tests
that originate from the Mastra project are adapted as black-box
specifications only, with import paths rewritten to @redtuma/*; verify the
upstream license of any such file before vendoring it under spec/.

This product builds on the Vercel AI SDK (`ai`) for low-level model and
tool-calling primitives, and uses zod, OpenTelemetry, and Hono.
